      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Loss of self-image hurts deeply, especially when identity has become intertwined with an ambitious life purpose. Try to reclaim a measure of self-worth by honoring the pain of your sacrifice; often, grief itself can become a profound motivator to rediscover a self beyond the theory. Reaching out to a grief counselor or a suicide prevention hotline is a critical step toward breaking this isolation and finding hope for a future self.",
      "source": "target",
